title: SC EP:270 Open Mics - Behind The Scenes
itunes:title: SC EP:270 Open Mics - Behind The Scenes
description: Duke and Woody join the show tonight. We left our mics on before our interview with Linda Godfrey on her research regarding Dogman to discuss some topics we never talk about on the air. We also discuss past encounters, and our take on what is going on the Bigfoot world.
